<caption id="DF125F9EA067FFC7FF10FBC6D4C6FB62" pageId="9" pageNumber="828" startId="9.[164,243,1145,1164]">
<paragraph id="8BD20F16A067FFC7FF10FBC6D4C6FB62" blockId="9.[164,1441,1145,1253]" pageId="9" pageNumber="828">
<emphasis id="B919D304A067FFC7FF10FBC6D644FB0B" bold="true" box="[164,268,1145,1165]" pageId="9" pageNumber="828">Figure 7.</emphasis>
Mitochondrial cytochrome 
<emphasis id="B919D304A067FFC7FD82FBC5D508FB0A" box="[566,576,1146,1164]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="828">c</emphasis>
oxidase subunit I (COI) haplotype variation of 53 noncontinuous sites obtained from the 
<taxonomicName id="4C6D7495A067FFC7FEBDFB28D6FCFB2C" box="[265,436,1175,1194]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Merodon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="828" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="avidus">
